{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Blind Man's Sun</strong> is a visual novel in the genres of psychological horror and supernatural mystery, done in an artsy pixel style. Together with Jack Collingwood, you'll embark on a journey to help his companion Iris recover her lost memories and uncover who condemned her to eternal torment.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Plot</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sometimes it feels like life\u2019s finally coming together. Money problems solved, your marriage is perfect, and your little girl\u2019s growing up happy and healthy. <br>Feels like it. <br>Then the fog clears, and you realize that &quot;happy life&quot; is just a bubble waiting to be popped by a drunk driver. <br>My wife died, and I ended up in a coma. Technically, I came out of it blind, but honestly... that\u2019s just the start.  <br>Too long to explain here. Check out the novel\u2014there\u2019s Iris, my possession, and the Midnight Sun.  <br>All the crazy stuff I got dragged into.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hope you enjoy the ride. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A unique combination of graphic styles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A story inspired by 2000s comic books.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A charismatic protagonist who will troll you. Yes, player, I'm talking about you.</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"My name is Iris. ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3201610/2235dff171aed31a9d9135c0279ec0c78e9367a0.jpg"},{"name":"I let Jack write it.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3201610/2235dff171aed31a9d9135c0279ec0c78e9367a0.jpg"},{"name":"You're going to follow the rules?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3201610/2235dff171aed31a9d9135c0279ec0c78e9367a0.jpg"},{"name":